oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Artist in Residence - Rosanne Cash - 2015-09-02
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: First of three Artist in Residence performances by Rosanne Cash and her band from the CMA Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on September 3, 2015. Special guests include Tony Joe White, Lucinda Williams and Cory Chisel.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Rosanne Cash; Tony Joe White; Lucinda Williams; Cory Chisel
